metadata.name: Wander[001] in Terminal
metadata.description:
Part of AI Public Art Project Wander[001]

Wander is a female android travelling on the future earth.
Send any real-world locations to Wander on discord, then you will receive your own interactive fiction. All contents are generated through AI based on real-world open data.

Project website: [www.wander001.com](http://www.wander001.com)
[Talk to Wander here](https://discord.gg/3njPKQJ4V4)
